OL,4,Chaven't chosen new ferry service
OL,5,Cprovider
OL,7,FKirsten Morel has explained why Jersey
OL,8,Fhasn't selected a new ferry service
OL,9,Fprovider yet.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Channel, Jersey's
OL,12,FMinister for Sustainable Economic
OL,13,FDevelopment claims the island is not
OL,14,Fat a position yet where they want to
OL,15,Fgo for a different operator to
OL,16,FGuernsey yet.
