OL,3,CKirsten Morel explains why Jersey
OL,4,Chaven't chosen new ferry service
OL,5,Cprovider
OL,7,FHe said: "We're not at the position of
OL,8,Fgoing with two operators. We're at the
OL,9,Fposition where Jersey wants and needs
OL,10,Fmore information from both operators
OL,11,Fto ensure things such as financial
OL,12,Fstability.
OL,14,F"We need to make sure we chose a
OL,15,Fprovider who can provide services for
OL,16,Fthe full 15 years. We don't want
OL,17,FJersey or Guernsey tax payers to be in
OL,18,Fa position where they are forced into
OL,19,Fsome rescue packages."
