OL,4,Chaven't chosen new ferry service
OL,5,Cprovider
OL,7,FIt comes amid reports that Condor
OL,8,Fasked the government for a loan of
OL,9,F#80M in the last year, with #10M
OL,10,Fneeded up front to secure their
OL,11,Fservices. This was allegedly rejected
OL,12,Fat the time.
OL,14,FWatch the full interview here...
