OL,3,CKirsten Morel explains why Jersey
OL,4,Chaven't chosen new ferry service
OL,5,Cprovider
OL,7,FWhen asked if he would pursue another
OL,8,Foperator if he can't get a guarantee
OL,9,Fthat Jersey taxpayers will not be
OL,10,Fresponsible for picking up a potential
OL,11,Frescue deal, he replied: "There's
OL,12,Flogic in that but not something I'm
OL,13,Fwilling to say at the moment."
