OL,3,CKirsten Morel explains why Jersey
OL,4,Chaven't chosen new ferry service
OL,5,Cprovider
OL,7,FDeputy Morel also added: "I'm not
OL,8,Fgoing to be pulled at the minute one
OL,9,Fway or the other (with who Jersey will
OL,10,Fselect). What I want to make sure is
OL,11,Fwhoever we appoint that they have the
OL,12,Ffinancial stability to last that 15
OL,13,Fyears, that really is for me the
OL,14,Fbottom line."
OL,16,FThe Minister then said: "I'm not angry
OL,17,Fwith Guernsey. I do understand that
OL,18,Fdifferent jurisdictions and different
OL,19,Fcountries have to look at their own
OL,20,Finterests.
