OL,3,CKirsten Morel explains why Jersey
OL,4,Chaven't chosen new ferry service
OL,5,Cprovider
OL,7,F"Guernsey has its perspective and
OL,8,Fthat's absolutely fine, but I am
OL,9,Fdetermined that Jersey tax payers know
OL,10,FI am acting for their benefit and on
OL,11,Ftheir behalf. That's the thing that
OL,12,Freally matters to me."
OL,14,FAfter this, he said he couldn't give a
OL,15,Ftimescale on when the decision would
OL,16,Fbe made.
